pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 150%\">从事自然资源大数据挖掘、知识图谱构建、知识应用开发等关键技术研发、数据分析处理、软件工具开发等相关工作。</span></p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"50\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 37.5pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: medium none; padding-right: 5.4pt\">\n            <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; text-indent: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%\">1</span></p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"140\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 105pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: medium none; padding-right: 5.4pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; text-indent: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%\">计算机或测绘与地理信息科学等相关专业。</span></p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"104\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 78pt; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: medium none; padding-right: 5.4pt\">\n            <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; text-indent: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 150%\">研究生/博士</span></p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"52\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; width: 39.5pt; 